---
title: Creamy Chicken and Rigatoni with Spinach
description: Juicy Italian-seasoned chicken takes centre stage and tops tonight's creamy masterpiece! Rounding out the cast of characters are the garlicky cream sauce, wilted spinach and savoury thyme ... need we say more!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rigatonis-au-poulet-cremeux-50e1bf98.jpg
